Web appication
open the drive and create a empty folder open vs code from it
now go to the terminal install packages
npm init
npm i dot env
npm i express
npm install sequelize
npm install mqsql2
create the file .env
now create the Config folder
inside it create the server.config.js file and make the port aviable write the code
now create a folder Routes
add index.js file in it
create a new folder controller and make category.controller and product.controller
npm install mysql2 and sequleize
create a database name ecomm_db from mysql
now create db.config.js in config folder and write in it
now create a model folder and create category.js and products.js in it and write code
npm i body-parser
